"{\"uid\": \"walb.com-2024-08-19-moultrie-welcome-home-carson-tyler-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Moultrie, Ga. (WALB) - The city of Moultrie is gearing up to welcome home Moultrie native Carson Tyler with a parade.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ga-Adangbe_people\", \"score\": 0.874706777597388, \"rank\": 0.141285546990253, \"text\": \"Ga\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ga-Adangbe_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ga-Adangbe_people\"}, {\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WALB\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3164269313523e-12, \"text\": \"WALB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WALB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WALB\"}, {\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Moultrie\", \"score\": 0.937853542012018, \"rank\": 0.06626456598111746, \"text\": \"Moultrie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Moultrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Moultrie\"}, {\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 96, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Carson\", \"score\": 0.9987976152825512, \"rank\": 0.0011522092783175799, \"text\": \"Carson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Carson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Carson\"}, {\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9994365058198116, \"rank\": 0.0005605019907481621, \"text\": \"Tyler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tyler is returning home today from Paris after competing in diving at the 2024 Summer Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 119, \"end\": 124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9994365058198116, \"rank\": 0.0005605019907481621, \"text\": \"Tyler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\"}, {\"begin\": 154, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999988744968472, \"rank\": 1.1255043729333198e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The city of Moltrie posted on its Facebook page that a parade will be taking place tonight at 6 p.m.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are asking residents to wear red, white, and blue to support Tyler.\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9994365058198116, \"rank\": 0.0005605019907481621, \"text\": \"Tyler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The parade route is set to start at 1st Street SE in Moultrie, and head towards East Central Avenue where it will take a left, and end on South Main Street near Kirbo Law.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 450, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Moultrie\", \"score\": 0.937853542012018, \"rank\": 0.06626456598111746, \"text\": \"Moultrie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Moultrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Moultrie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the parade wraps up, Tyler will go on a stage and the city will read a proclamation in his honor.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9994365058198116, \"rank\": 0.0005605019907481621, \"text\": \"Tyler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will then be presented a key to the city.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once that wraps up, Tyler will be available to take pictures and sign autographs.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9994365058198116, \"rank\": 0.0005605019907481621, \"text\": \"Tyler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tyler placed 4th in theMen's 3-meter Diving event, and he also competed in the Men's 10-meter diving event.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 803, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9994365058198116, \"rank\": 0.0005605019907481621, \"text\": \"Tyler\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have a news tip or see an error that needs correction?Let us know.Please include the article's headline in your message.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To stay up to date on all the latest news as it develops, follow WALB onFacebookandX (Twitter).\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more South Georgia news, download the WALB News app from theA